Harry Greaves, executive director at Prospect Resources, discusses the company's Arcadia lithium project in Zimbabwe and why investors should have the company on their radar. Prospect’s flagship project is the Arcadia Lithium Project located is on the outskirts of Harare in Zimbabwe. The Arcadia Lithium Project represents a globally significant hard rock lithium resource and is being rapidly developed by Prospect’s experienced team, focusing on near term production of petalite, spodumene and tantalum concentrates.